'''桑寄生植物'''又称'''槲寄生植物'''，是一类可以进行[[光合作用|光合作用]]的半寄生[[灌木|灌木]]，包括[[檀香目|檀香目]]下的[[桑寄生科|桑寄生科]]、[[槲寄生科|槲寄生科]]、[[羽毛果科|羽毛果科]]、[[榄仁檀科|榄仁檀科]]和部分[[檀香科|檀香科]]植物，共有88个[[属|属]], 约1,600种植物<ref name="biods.2019350">{{cite journal |last1=Li |first1=Manru |last2=Zhang |first2=Ling |title=Overview of the reproductive phenology of mistletoes |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-07-20 |volume=28 |issue=7 |pages=833 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019350}}</ref>。除极地、部分高寒和干旱沙漠地区外均有分布<ref>{{cite book |last1=Watson |first1=David M. |title=Mistletoes of Southern Australia |publisher=CSIRO Pub |location=Collingwood, Vic. |isbn=978-0-643-10225-5 |url=https://ebooks.publish.csiro.au/content/mistletoes-southern-australia |accessdate=2020-12-20 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126143819/https://ebooks.publish.csiro.au/content/mistletoes-southern-australia |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大部分桑寄生植物都能够产生[[花蜜|花蜜]]和大量颜色鲜艳的[[果实|果实]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Watson |first1=David M. |last2=Herring |first2=Matthew |title=Mistletoe as a keystone resource: an experimental test |journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences |date=2012-09-22 |volume=279 |issue=1743 |pages=3853–3860 |doi=10.1098/rspb.2012.0856}}</ref>，以便依靠[[鸟类|鸟类]]或[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]散播[[种子|种子]]<ref name="biods.2019350" />。

